        <h1 id="product-title">
          <span class="product-name">Huawei OptiXstar</span>
          <span class="product-model">B896-U6</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="product-intro">
          把全光网络、无线覆盖与视频存储，收进同一台融合网关。
        </p>
        <div class="product-tags" aria-label="产品能力">
          <span>FTTO 全光接入</span>
          <span>Wi-Fi 7</span>
          <span>NVR 融合</span>
          <span>4T / 8T 存储</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="product-visual" data-reveal>
        <div class="product-stage" data-product-stage>
          <div class="product-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="signal-ring signal-ring--one" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="signal-ring signal-ring--two" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <img
            src="/images/product/huawei-optixstar-b896-u6.webp"
            width="2357"
            height="2054"
            alt="Huawei OptiXstar B896-U6 视频融合网关"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            data-product-image
          />
          <p class="product-stage-caption">
            <span>01</span>
            视频融合网关
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="product-scroll-hint" href="#product-capabilities" aria-label="继续了解产品能力">
        <span>向下探索</span>
        <span class="product-scroll-line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="product-problem" aria-labelledby="product-problem-title">
      <div class="product-section-heading" data-reveal>
        <p>ONE DEVICE, ONE SYSTEM</p>
        <h2 id="product-problem-title">让网络与安防，不再各自为战。</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="product-problem-grid">
        <div class="product-problem-copy" data-reveal>
          <p>
            传统小型园区或门店常常同时部署光网络设备、无线路由、录像机与独立存储。
            设备多、布线杂、管理入口分散，后续扩容也更复杂。
          </p>
          <p>
            B896-U6 将连接、覆盖与录像能力融合到一个设备形态中，
            用更简洁的架构承载办公网络与视频安防。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-problem-side" data-reveal>
          <figure class="problem-visual">
            <img
              src="/images/product/feature-fiber.webp"
              width="1600"
              height="900"
              alt="光纤连接企业网络设备的特写"
              loading="lazy"
            />
